SystemScripts.Name: Add MKV extension to files without an extension
SystemScripts.Description:
Monitors the directories listed in the variable AddExtensionDirectoryList and any file thats found without an extenion, MKV will be added to it
/

SystemScripts.Name: Delete Empty Folders

Reads a variable 'DeleteEmptyFolders' and iterates all folders defined there and will delete any empty folder found within, leaving the root folder

SystemScripts.Name: SABnzbd - Pause Downloads
SystemScripts.Description:
Pauses SABnzbd if the current file processing queue is greater than 30 files.  If the processing queue is not greater than 30 files, then it will resume SABnzbd
/

SystemScripts.Name: Delete Rogue _UNPACK_ Directories
SystemScripts.Description:
Will check any _UNPACK_ directories, and if they haven't be modified in 24 hours will delete that directory

FlowScripts.Name: Video - Dolby Vision - Fix crop and compatibility
FlowScripts.Description:
Converts to the most compatibile profile 8.1 and removing bad crop data.
Run between encode and move/replace.
Output is always an MKV.
dovi_tool only supports HEVC when AV1 support is added I will updated this script.

FlowScripts.Name: Video - Filesize bigger than calculated
FlowScripts.Description:
Determines a maximum filesize by the given GB/h comma-separated list for 4k, 1080p, 720p, SD (e.g. 15.5,4,2,1) and returns if the input file is bigger or not.
 It calculates the filesize using the actual runtime of the input file and compares it against the actual file size

SubFlows.Name: Disable HW HEVC CPU
SubFlows.Description:
Disabled all hardware devices and will encode videos using HEVC CPU.
Will execute the FFmpeg Builder Executor but does not initiate the FFmpeg Builder Start,
SubFlows.Author: reven

SubFlows.Name: HEVC AC3 Encode
SubFlows.Description:
Converts a video to HEVC with AC3 audio.
Will automatically crop black bars if detected.
Will re-encode a file at a lower quality if file size increases.
Uses `Disable HW HEVC CPU` to reattempt encoding if hardware encoding fails.
SubFlows.Author: reven
